name: Abyssin Ornament & Wounded Wookiee (V)
Text: 'USED: Creature attacks at pits are immune to At Peace and Yarna d''al'' Gargan until end of your next turn. (Immune to Sense) OR Cancel an attempt to target a rancor with a character weapon. OR Use 1 Force (2 if a rancor on table) to deploy Nal Hutta from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.STARTING: If Great Pit Of Carkoon on table, deploy from Reserve Deck an Effect that is always immune to Alter and choose to deploy from Reserve Deck: Rancor Pit and a rancor there, OR Power Of The Hutt and Sarlacc. Place this Interrupt in hand.(Original concept by Proofing Team - PC Volunteer Award 2007)',
